# Dental Receptionist Chatbot

An AI-powered dental clinic receptionist chatbot built with FastAPI and Groq.

## Features
- Answers patient questions based on clinic-specific data
- RAG (Retrieval Augmented Generation) for accurate responses
- Clean chat UI embeddable on any website
- Supports multiple clinics with separate data

## Tech Stack
- **Backend**: Python, FastAPI
- **AI**: Groq API (Llama 3.3)
- **RAG**: Custom keyword search
- **Frontend**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

## Setup

1. Clone the repository
```
   git clone https://github.com/tabraiz-2005/dental-chatbot.git
   cd dental-chatbot
```

2. Create virtual environment
```
   python3 -m venv venv
   source venv/bin/activate
```

3. Install dependencies
```
   pip install fastapi uvicorn groq python-dotenv
```

4. Create .env file
```
   GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
```

5. Add clinic data to clinic_data.txt

6. Run the server
```
   uvicorn main:app --reload
```

7. Open http://127.0.0.1:8000/app

## Deployment
Deployed on Railway. Set GROQ_API_KEY in Railway environment variables.

## Project Structure
```
dental-chatbot/
├── main.py          # FastAPI backend
├── rag.py           # RAG search engine
├── index.html       # Chat frontend
├── clinic_data.txt  # Clinic information
├── Procfile         # Railway deployment config
└── requirements.txt # Python dependencies
```

## Roadmap
- [ ] Clinic admin upload page
